article_title: Azerbaijan says Doha draft sees oil production frozen until October: TASS
article_text:
The minister, Natig Aliyev, described the draft as a "gentlemen's" agreement.

Aliyev was not available for immediate comment when called by Reuters.

(Reporting by Polina Devitt and Nailia Bagirova; Editing by Richard Balmforth)
